name: Opening Ceremony
tips_dialog: Senpai, please pay attention to the time. The opening ceremony is about to begin.

name: Newbies
tips_dialog: Senpai, be careful where you walk!| It's my fault... Are you injured?

name: House Human
tips_dialog: Senpai! What is.. This test?

name: House Monster
tips_dialog: Iron Fist, listen to Senpai when he suggested for you to go to House Monster. |Isn't that right, Senpai? Isn't their examination spot right in front of it?

name: House Angel
tips_dialog: I've been waiting for almost a day. I thought you were in trouble at House Monster.

name: Elf of House Fairy
tips_dialog: Are you going to the exam site that Kong Ming is in charge of afterwards?

name: Fallen Angel of House Demon
tips_dialog: Ah, House Demon... Sounds terrible... | Haha, it's all right. Don't worry, Iron Fist. Lucifer is actually a pretty cool person.

name: House Ghost
tips_dialog: Vampires? They are no different from House Demons just now...
